ZH: 我们今晚要去一家新的餐厅吃晚饭。
EN: We are going to a new restaurant for dinner tonight.

ZH: 这家餐厅提供很多不同种类的美食。
EN: This restaurant offers a variety of different types of cuisine.

ZH: 餐厅里的服务员都很有礼貌。
EN: The waitstaff at the restaurant are all very polite.

ZH: 我最喜欢的餐厅是那家烤肉店。
EN: My favorite restaurant is that BBQ place.

ZH: 这家餐厅的环境非常优雅。
EN: The atmosphere at this restaurant is very elegant.

ZH: 我们在餐厅里订了一桌。
EN: We reserved a table at the restaurant.

ZH: 餐厅里的菜单有中文和英文两种。
EN: The menu at the restaurant is in both Chinese and English.

ZH: 这家餐厅的生煎包特别好吃。
EN: The pan-fried dumplings at this restaurant are especially delicious.

ZH: 我们可以在餐厅外面吃。
EN: We can eat outside the restaurant.

ZH: 餐厅里的音乐很轻柔。
EN: The music in the restaurant is very soothing.

ZH: 这家餐厅的装修风格很现代。
EN: The decor style of this restaurant is very modern.

ZH: 这家餐厅离我家很远。
EN: This restaurant is far from my home.

ZH: 餐厅里有一个开放式厨房。
EN: The restaurant has an open kitchen.

ZH: 这家餐厅每周都会有新的特色菜品。
EN: This restaurant features new dishes every week.

ZH: 我们可以在餐厅里吃到地道的中餐。
EN: We can have authentic Chinese food at this restaurant.

ZH: 这家餐厅的厨师很有名气。
EN: The chef at this restaurant is very famous.

ZH: 在这家餐厅工作了两年后，我学到了很多东西。
EN: I learned a lot after working at this restaurant for two years.

ZH: 老板决定关闭这家餐厅。
EN: The boss decided to close down the restaurant.

ZH: 餐厅提供送餐服务。
EN: The restaurant offers delivery service.

ZH: 我们在餐厅见面吧。
EN: Let's meet at the restaurant.
